The Dennis Prager Radio Show JUN-10-2014 TUES


Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20140610  3 Ultimate Issues Hour: Rebbe

Prager H3: Dennis talks to Joseph Telushkin, 
             an American rabbi, lecturer, and author. 

      His new book is, 
         Rebbe: The Life and Teachings of Menachem M. Schneerson, 
            The Most Influential Rabbi in Modern History.


Prager 20140610  2 New Shooting

Prager H2: Yet another murder at a high school. 
             This time in Oregon. Dennis comments 

       Dennis talks to Steve Forbes, chairman of Forbes Media.


Prager 20140610  1 Colorless

Prager H1: Dennis wonders: where are all the brightly colored cars?

        Seems like all the cars on the road are black, white or silver?

                       Callers weigh in.
